{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Deadly Days: Roadtrip</strong> is an exciting action roguelite, that combines reverse bullet hell gameplay with strategic inventory management. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Start your road trip through the zombie apocalypse! Fight your way through, gain experience and collect items to assemble an epic inventory. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Craft more effective weapons and find out what items you can combine to withstand the ever-increasing waves of zombies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026450/extras/dd_roadtrip_s_01.png?t=1737369692\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">A well-organized inventory is your best life insurance:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Arrange your weapons and items in such a way that you maximize synergies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use your workbench to craft new gear or increase the rarity level of your items.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Find particularly exciting items in airdrops, which you receive for every level-up in battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026450/extras/dd_roadtrip_s_03.png?t=1737369692\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Each of your trips is different:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is partly due to your choice of destination and partly due to the procedurally generated maps. The meta-progression will help you to master even the most difficult routes. The future is uncertain. Can you alter the course, escape the danger, or find a way to survive? It's all up to you now.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026450/extras/dd_roadtrip_s_02.png?t=1737369692\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Deadly Days: Roadtrip \u2013 Your Ultimate Solo Adventure!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">One Hero, One Journey. Each run you can choose out of 10+ unlockable characters with unique abilities and weapons. Walking your path alone brings deep wisdom, yet the bonds you form with new and old friends are just as sacred. You will need their exceptional talents and starting weapons. They will be available for selection on your next run after you have rescued them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Choose from different roadtrip destinations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Fight through hordes of zombies and take on boss battles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> On your journey loot stuff, combine items in your inventory and craft new weapons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Find survivors and unlock new characters for your next run</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Become more powerful across multiple runs by earning meta upgrades.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Unlock new destinations and choose suitable characters and equipment for your next run</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Diverse, procedurally generated maps</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> 10+ unlockable survivors with individual skills</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> A large selection of base items</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> A wide range of item combinations</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">GIFs:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026450/extras/DeutscheIndieShowcaseExclusivedd_r_playtest3_trailer_v8mp4-ezgif.com-optimize__3_.gif?t=1737369692\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026450/extras/DeutscheIndieShowcaseExclusivedd_r_playtest3_trailer_v8mp4-ezgif.com-o